description: Try our easy to follow Quick Mexican Chicken Quesadillas recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
keywords: Quesadilla,Seafood free,Tree nut free,Egg free,Spring,Low sugar,Sesame free,High protein,Sandwich press,Quick & easy lunch,Chicken,Dinner Made Easy,Peanut free
name: Quick Mexican Chicken Quesadillas Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 500g Cook chicken breast strips Mexican style

recipeInstructions.text: Preheat oven to 160°C/140°C fan-forced. Heat oil in a frying pan over medium-high heat and cook chicken, stirring, for 5 minutes or until cooked through. Transfer to a chopping board and roughly chop.

Preheat a sandwich press. Place 1 tortilla on a flat surface. Top with one-fifth of chicken. Scatter over one-fifth of onion and 1/4 cup cheese. Top with another tortilla. Repeat with remaining tortillas, chicken, onion and cheese to make 5 quesadillas.
Place 1 quesadilla in sandwich press and cook for 2 minutes or until golden and heated through. Transfer to a baking tray and place in oven to keep warm. Repeat with remaining quesadillas.
Cut quesadillas into pieces and serve scattered with extra onion.
